title: Streets.Of.Rage.Remake.PSP.zip
description:
STREETS OF RAGE REMAKE FOR PSP


Genre: Beat'em up
Players: 1-2 or with CPU friend
Platforms: Windows 7 (32 bit), Windows 7 (64 bit), Windows Vista (32 bit), Windows Vista (64 bit), Windows XP
Manufacturer: Bombergames
Version: PSP

Streets of Rage Remake for PSP

This is not a port, but it is a system that allows you to use the PSP as a PC monitor and you can play by simply connecting a USB cable.
The file contains detailed instructions and everything you need for a perfect work with excellent quality on the Psp
